NK015(ba)020:0: sh+r+ai ba dz+ra ku m+aa ra s+ya sh+ai r+sha s+ya da sha sti //
NK015(ba)020:2: / dpal rdo rje gzhon nu'i dbu'i phyogs lags so //
NK015(ba)020:3: shes bya ma lus yongs rdzogs shing /
NK015(ba)020:5: / 'jig rten mun pa'i tshogs bcom pa //
NK015(ba)020:6: sgron ma gsal ba'i zhabs la 'dud //
NK015(ba)020:7: dpal gsum nyid ldan dgyes pa rnam gnyis kyi //
NK015(ba)020:8: chags gnyis mi gtong 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK015(ba)020:9: rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku la gnyis med mos //
NK015(ba)020:10: slob dpon pad+ma'i rgyal po rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i skyes bus /
NK015(ba)020:11: phur pa'i man ngag gi rtsa ba ngan sngags bton pa /
NK015(ba)020:12: tshig nyung la don che ba /
NK015(ba)020:13: shin tu zab pa'i man ngag 'di la /
NK015(ba)020:17: thugs phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK015(ba)020:20: dang po bden pa bdar zhing mtshams bcad pa dang /
NK015(ba)020:22: ting nge 'dzin rnam gsum sgom pa dang /
NK015(ba)020:24: brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK015(ba)020:25: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor gzhugs pa dang /
NK015(ba)020:30: don dang po bden pa bdar zhing mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK015(ba)020:33: gsang sngags kyi byin gyis rlabs so //
NK015(ba)020:35: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba b+hig+hana bam h'u phata /
NK015(ba)020:37: skad cig gi ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK015(ba)020:38: bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje gzhon nu'i skur bskyed do //
NK015(ba)020:40: sku mdog mthing nag zhabs bzhi bsgrad pa /
NK015(ba)020:44: phyag drug kas phur bu dril te /
NK015(ba)020:45: dang po gnyis kyis phur pa dkar po dril ba /
NK015(ba)020:46: bar ma gnyis kyis dmar po dril ba /
NK015(ba)020:47: tha ma gnyis kyis mthing nag dril ba /
NK015(ba)020:48: rdo rje'i gshog pa gdengs pa /
NK015(ba)020:49: dpal gyi chas brgyad dang dur khrod kyi chas brgyad dang ldan pa /
NK015(ba)020:50: mtshams rngams gzi byin dang ldan pa /
NK015(ba)020:51: skal pa'i me dpung gi nang na bzhugs pa /
NK015(ba)020:52: skad cig gis gsal bar bskyed do //
NK015(ba)020:53: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad bsdus te bdag la thim par bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)020:54: h'u rdo rje gsang ba'i bka' las ni //
NK015(ba)020:55: sdig can gang zhig 'da' byed pa //
NK015(ba)020:56: stobs chen khro bo chen po bcus //
NK015(ba)020:57: glad pa tshal pa brgya ru khos //
NK015(ba)020:58: nyon cig bgegs dang log 'dren tshogs //
NK015(ba)020:59: nga yi bka' la 'da' ma byed //
NK015(ba)020:60: khro bo bcu'i sngags dang de'i steng la /
NK015(ba)020:61: h'u ma ma pa sham ku ru ma stam nya
NK015(ba)020:62: na ka ra i d+ha na d+ha ti ma ma
NK015(ba)020:63: karma sh+ri kram ka ra ye h'u phata /
NK015(ba)020:64: ces tshar gcig brjod pa tsam gyis /
NK015(ba)020:65: thugs ka nas khro bo mthing nag gcer bu phyag
NK015(ba)020:66: na phur bu bsnams pa me dpung gi nang na
NK015(ba)020:69: phyogs bcu'i bgegs thams cad chung ba rnams che ba la bstim ste /
NK015(ba)020:70: bgegs kyi gtso bo phyogs skyongs bcu la bstim nas /
NK015(ba)020:71: khro bo bcus so sor bkug nas /
NK015(ba)020:72: rang gi phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi dang brgyad /
NK015(ba)020:73: mdun rgyab gnyis dang bcur bkug nas /
NK015(ba)020:75: 'og rdo rje'i brag ri la thal byung bar bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)020:76: phur pa'i dbal rtse la me 'bar ba dang phyogs skyong bcu yang mer lam gyis 'bar ba dang /
NK015(ba)020:77: de ltar khro bo bcu'i sku la lhag pa'i ye shes kyi me 'bar ba dang /
NK015(ba)020:78: 1 phyag gi phur pa la lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi me 'bar ba dang /
NK015(ba)020:79: 2 phyogs skyong rnams tshig pa la rnam rtog ye shes su 'bar ba'i me dang /
NK015(ba)020:80: 3 de gsum 'dres pa la me ri 'bar ba'i gur du bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)020:81: spyi don gnyis pa bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK015(ba)020:83: rdo rje gzhon nu'i dkyil 'khor gzhal yas khang dang bcas pa spyan drangs te /
NK015(ba)020:84: bdag gi mdun du bzhugs par bsam la /
NK015(ba)020:85: gtso bo'i dbu gtsug tu pad+ma zla ba'i gdan la bla ma bzhugs par bsgom zhing /
NK015(ba)020:86: ye shes sku mchog ces pa'i bshags pa bya /
NK015(ba)020:87: ting nge 'dzin ni rang dang mdun gyi dkyil 'khor
NK015(ba)020:88: bla ma dang bcas pa'i bar 'od rnam pa lngas
NK015(ba)020:89: 'brel bar bsam / tshigs bcad thon nas lha dang bla mas sdig pa dag go //
NK015(ba)020:90: nyes pa tshangs zhes pa'i gsung byung bar bsgom zhing
NK015(ba)020:91: 'od du zhu ste rang nyid la thim par bsam
NK015(ba)020:92: pa ni / byin rlabs bsdu ba'o //
NK015(ba)020:93: spyi don gsum pa ting nge 'dzin rnam gsum rim bzhin bsgom pa ni /
NK015(ba)020:94: rdo rje khros pas zhe sdang gcod //
NK015(ba)020:96: rdo rje ni rdo rje gzhon nu'o //
NK015(ba)020:97: khros pa ni ram yam kham gsum spros /
NK015(ba)020:98: zhe sdang ni gzung yul te /
NK015(ba)020:99: 'dir me chu rlung gsum gyis mi gnas par byas pa la ni gcod ces bya'o //
NK015(ba)020:101: bdag nyid rdo rje gzhon nu'i thugs ka nas /
NK015(ba)020:102: ram dmar po spros te me byung bas 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad ma lus pa bsregs /
NK015(ba)020:103: slar me'i lhag ma thugs ka na tshur bsdu /
NK015(ba)020:104: thugs ka nas yam spros te rlung byung nas /
NK015(ba)020:105: slar sngar bsregs pa'i thal ba ma lus pa 'thor bar byas /
NK015(ba)020:106: slar rlung gi lhag ma thugs ka nas tshur bsdu //
NK015(ba)020:107: yang thugs ka nas kham spros pas /
NK015(ba)020:108: chu byung bas lhag ma ma lus par bkrus te /
NK015(ba)020:109: chu'i lhag ma rnams bdag gi thugs kar tshur bsdu'o //
NK015(ba)020:110: de ltar gcod pa la ni mtshon ces bya ste /
NK015(ba)020:111: dper na 'jig rten gyi mtshon ral gri la sogs
NK015(ba)020:112: pas ni phyogs re re bas mi chod pa la
NK015(ba)020:113: / 'dir me chu rlung gsum gyis snod bcud rang
NK015(ba)020:114: sa med par byas pa la ni mtshon chen zhes
NK015(ba)020:115: / bya'o // sngon po ni cir yang mi 'gyur
NK015(ba)020:116: ba yin pas 'dir bsreg sbyangs rnam gsum gyis gzung
NK015(ba)020:118: bar der 'dzin sems kyang ma grub ste /
NK015(ba)020:119: ci yang mi dmigs pa stong pa nyid du bsgom par bya'o //
NK015(ba)020:120: de yang stong pa nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK015(ba)020:121: chos nyid ci yang mi dmigs pa las /
NK015(ba)020:122: chos can ci yang mi 'gyur ba ste /
NK015(ba)020:123: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin ces bya'o /
NK015(ba)020:125: / 'bar ba ni kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin te /
NK015(ba)020:126: stong nyid kyi ngang la de ltar ma rtogs pa'i sems can rnams la /
NK015(ba)020:128: nam mkha'i dkyil nas thig pa shar ba ni /
NK015(ba)020:130: chos nyid nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang las /
NK015(ba)020:131: rang gi rnam par shes pa'i ngo bo /
NK015(ba)020:132: h'u mthing nag gcig thig pa lta bu rang shar du byung ba'o //
NK015(ba)020:133: spyi don bzhi pa brten bskyed pa ni /
NK015(ba)020:134: srog gi go ru shar ba dang /
NK015(ba)020:136: srog ni 'byung ba lnga yin te /
NK015(ba)020:137: 'dir yang de gnas su dag pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)020:141: 'og gi phyogs su chos 'byung gru gsum pa kha dog mthing nag rgya che ba gcig bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)020:142: h'u las yam chad pa las /
NK015(ba)020:143: rlung gi dkyil 'khor gzhu'i dbyibs can rgya khyon che ba chos 'byung gi dkyil du bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)020:144: h'u las ram chad pa las me'i dkyil 'khor gru gsum pa'o //
NK015(ba)020:145: ra chad pa las rak+ta khrag gi rgya mtsho rba rlabs 'khrugs pa dbyibs zlum pa'o //
NK015(ba)020:146: mam chad pa la mam sa'i sa gzhi ste /
NK015(ba)020:147: sha chen gyi thang ma bdal ba dbyibs gru bzhi pa'o //
NK015(ba)020:148: kem chad pa las kem rus kyi ri rab nag po kha khyer gyen du che ba /
NK015(ba)020:149: bya sha zan mang po lding ba /
NK015(ba)020:151: rak+ta khrag gi zham chu 'bab pa /
NK015(ba)020:153: yang h'u las h'u chad pa las /
NK015(ba)020:154: ri rab kyi kha la bab ste /
NK015(ba)020:156: rdo rje rgya gram du gyur te /
NK015(ba)020:161: lte ba mthing nag h'u gis mtshan pa'o //
NK015(ba)020:162: h'u badz+ra ma h+aa rak+sha rak+sha h'u /
NK015(ba)020:165: rdo rje'i gur khang mthing nag rgya khyon che bar gyur to //
NK015(ba)020:166: yang h'u las b+h+r+aum chad de 'od du zhu ba las /
NK015(ba)020:167: dur khrod kyi gzhal yas khang du gyur te /
NK015(ba)020:168: gru bzhi pa sgo bzhi pa /
NK015(ba)020:169: phyi thod pa skam po las brtsigs pa /
NK015(ba)020:171: nang thod rlon las brtsigs pa /
NK015(ba)020:173: lhor rin po ches brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)020:176: steng spyi bsdus rdo rje rtse dgu pa'i bum par 'khyil ba /
NK015(ba)020:177: steng thams cad rdo rje mthing nag gi brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)020:178: 'og gzhi e khrom nyi shu rtsa gcig lha snam dang bcas pa'o //
NK015(ba)020:179: gzhal yas khang gi rgyan yang smon lam gyi shugs dang ma bral ba'am /
NK015(ba)020:180: gdul bya'i bskul ba gsan pa'i rtags su skal pa'i lung nag 'tshubs pa /
NK015(ba)020:181: ye shes kyi me ri phyi nang med par 'bar ba /
NK015(ba)020:182: sprul pa phyogs bcur 'phros pa'i rtags su rdo rje rtse lnga'i thog mnga' 'phro ba /
NK015(ba)020:183: dngos po thams cad sems su rtogs pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)020:184: tsit+ta'i phol phying gis brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)020:185: dug gsum gnas su dag pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)020:186: sbrul nag gi za ra tshag gis brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)020:187: chos thams cad bdag med par rtogs pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)020:189: zhi gnas lhag mthong zung du 'brel ba'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)020:190: nyi zla'i skar khung yod pa /
NK015(ba)020:191: thugs rjes chags pa dang ma bral ba'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)020:193: rgyal chen bzhi la sgo'i ru bzhi byas pa /
NK015(ba)020:194: gnam lcags kyi ya them yod pa /
NK015(ba)020:195: ma them khro chu la byas pa /
NK015(ba)020:196: lha chen brgyad kyis ka ba /
NK015(ba)020:197: klu chen brgyad kyis gdung ma /
NK015(ba)020:198: gza' dang rgyu skar gyis kha bad byas pa /
NK015(ba)020:204: dbus su ru tra pho mo dang /
NK015(ba)020:205: ma h+aa de ba pho mo bsnol ba'i zhabs na pad+ma zla ba nyi ma brtsegs pa'o //
NK015(ba)020:209: e khram nyi shu la khro bo bdu'i gdan nyi
NK015(ba)020:210: ma bcu'i thog tu phyogs skyongs kyi ro pho mo
NK015(ba)020:211: bsnol ba ni / shar brgya byin pho mo /
NK015(ba)020:213: shar lho me lha pho mo /
NK015(ba)020:217: lho nub srin po pho mo /
NK015(ba)020:221: nub byang rlung lha pho mo /
NK015(ba)020:225: byang shar dbang ldan pho mo /
NK015(ba)020:229: rgyab tu sa bdag pho mo /
NK015(ba)020:234: dam can gyi gnas su ro mgo med pa bcu gnyis bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)020:235: spyi don lnga pa brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa la bzhi ste /
NK015(ba)020:237: phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK015(ba)020:238: phur pa sras kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK015(ba)020:239: dam can srungs ma'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK015(ba)020:240: de yang bdag rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK015(ba)020:241: nam mkha'i h'u de dbus kyi gdan thog tu bab pa las /
NK015(ba)020:245: rdo rje nag po rtse dgu pa lte ba h'u gis mtshan pa'o //
NK015(ba)020:246: de las 'od zer 'phros bskul don gnyis byas /
NK015(ba)020:247: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud bskul /
NK015(ba)020:248: sems can gyi lus ngag yid gsum gyi sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK015(ba)020:250: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK015(ba)020:252: rdo rje gzhon nu'i skur gyur te /
NK015(ba)020:253: snying gi go ru bsgom par bya //
NK015(ba)020:255: rdo rje h'u dang bcas pa'o //
NK015(ba)020:256: snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig ni //
NK015(ba)020:258: 'jig rten pa bzhin zhe sdang gis bsad cing /
NK015(ba)020:259: gti mug gis mnan pa ma yin no /
NK015(ba)020:261: / 'od 'phros pas sems can thams cad kyi lus ngag yid gsum gyi sgrib pa sbyangs nas /
NK015(ba)020:262: rdo rje gzhon nu'i skur gyur pa ni /
NK015(ba)020:263: phung po rdo rje gtam byas nas //
NK015(ba)020:266: rdo rje gzhon nu'i skur gyur pa ni /
NK015(ba)020:267: rnam par shes pa rdo rje bsgom //
NK015(ba)020:274: rdo rje'i gshog pa gdengs pa /
NK015(ba)020:277: dbus mthing nag sku dang mthun pa /
NK015(ba)020:278: phyag drug gi g.yas kyi dang po na /
NK015(ba)020:279: ye shes kyi rdo rje rtse dgu pa bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)020:280: bar ma na rtse lnga pa /
NK015(ba)020:281: g.yon dang po na me dpung /
NK015(ba)020:282: bar ma na kha t+w+aam bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)020:283: tha ma gnyis na ri rab lta bu'i phur pa dril ba'o //
NK015(ba)020:284: dbu skra khams nag gyen du bardzesa pa /
NK015(ba)020:285: dbu re re la thod pa skam po lnga lngas brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)020:286: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas dbu la bzhugs pa /
NK015(ba)020:287: sku stod la glang chen gyi ko rlon /
NK015(ba)020:288: sku smad la stag gi sham thabs byas pa /
NK015(ba)020:289: zhing lpags kyis sked chings byas pa /
NK015(ba)020:290: thod rlon lnga bcu rtsa gcig gi phreng ba se ral khar thogs pa /
NK015(ba)020:291: sbrul dkar pos dbu dang sku la brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)020:292: ser pos snyan cha byas pa /
NK015(ba)020:294: nag pos rkang rgyan byas pa /
NK015(ba)020:295: zhag gis zo ris khur ba la /
NK015(ba)020:296: rak+ta'i thig le brang dang kha la /
NK015(ba)020:297: thal ba'i tshom bu thal gong la brgyan pa'o //
NK015(ba)020:298: yan lag la keng rus kyis brgyan pa'o //
NK015(ba)020:299: dpung pa la thod pa ra ri dang /
NK015(ba)020:301: zhabs g.yas brkyang pas thabs chen pos 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'o //
NK015(ba)020:302: g.yon bskum pa ni shes rab kyi dbyings rtogs kyang /
NK015(ba)020:303: mya ngan las 'das pa'i mtha' las mi gnas pa'o //
NK015(ba)020:304: yang na g.yas bskum pa ni /
NK015(ba)020:305: thabs thugs rje chen pos 'gro ba'i don mdzad na yang /
NK015(ba)020:306: chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos shing 'khor ba'i mtha' ma gos pa'i rtags so //
NK015(ba)020:308: thugs rjes 'gro ba'i don mdzad na yang /
NK015(ba)020:309: chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos pa'i rtags so //
NK015(ba)020:311: lus dang grib ma'i tshul du /
NK015(ba)020:312: yab grub na yum grub ste /
NK015(ba)020:315: g.yon thod khrag rgyan cha lugs rnams yab dang 'dra ba la /
NK015(ba)020:318: yab kyi thugs kar ye shes sems dpa' rang 'dra ba /
NK015(ba)020:319: de'i thugs kar rdo rje h'u dang bcas pa'o //
NK015(ba)020:321: de'i nang du zla ba'i steng du h'u las /
NK015(ba)020:322: tip+ta ha tsakra ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u gis g.yon du 'khor ba'o //
NK015(ba)020:323: gnyis pa phyogs bcu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK015(ba)020:324: yab yum gyi mkha' gsang byin gyis rlabs te /
NK015(ba)020:325: yab kyi gsang gnas su ma las nyi ma'i steng du /
NK015(ba)020:326: rdo rje nag po rtse dgu pa'i lte ba la h'u /
NK015(ba)020:330: pam las pad+ma dmar po 'dab ma brgyad pa'i ze'u 'bru la am dmar pos mtshan pa'o //
NK015(ba)020:332: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad bsdus nas rang gi zhal du zhugs /
NK015(ba)020:333: sku'i dbyib tu brgyud yab yum gnyis ma chags thabs kyi rol pa mdzad pas /
NK015(ba)020:334: yum gyi mkha' la phab ste /
NK015(ba)020:335: h'u sgril ma bcur gyur te /
NK015(ba)020:337: phyogs skyongs bcu'i gdan steng du bab pa las /
NK015(ba)020:338: badz+ra kro d+ha h'u ka ra h'u /
NK015(ba)020:341: mdun gyi e khram gyi steng du khro bo chen po h'u mdzad dang /
NK015(ba)020:343: de'i mchan g.yon phyogs su sprul pa'i phra men ma /
NK015(ba)020:346: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya h'u /
NK015(ba)020:347: ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK015(ba)020:348: shar phyogs su khro bo chen po rnam par rgyal ba dang /
NK015(ba)020:349: yum rdo rje snyems ma sprul pa stag dang bya rgod kyi mgo can no //
NK015(ba)020:350: badz+ra kro d+ha ni la dan+da h'u /
NK015(ba)020:351: da ha da ha h'u phata /
NK015(ba)020:352: shar lho khro bo chen po dbyug sngon can dang /
NK015(ba)020:354: sprul pa g.yag dang bya rog gi mgo can no //
NK015(ba)020:355: badz+ra kro d+ha ya man+ta ka h'u /
NK015(ba)020:356: pa tsa pa tsa h'u phata /
NK015(ba)020:357: lhor khro bo chen po gshin rje gshed po dang /
NK015(ba)020:359: sprul pa sha ba dang 'ug pa'i mgo can no //
NK015(ba)020:360: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h'u /
NK015(ba)020:362: lho nub tu khro bo chen po mi g.yo mgon po dang /
NK015(ba)020:363: yum rdo rje gtum khung ma /
NK015(ba)020:364: sprul pa gzig dang khwa ta'i mgo can no //
NK015(ba)020:365: badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+h+ri wa h'u /
NK015(ba)020:366: hu lu hu lu h'u phata /
NK015(ba)020:367: nub tu khro bo chen po rta mgrin dang /
NK015(ba)020:369: sprul pa byi la dang pu shud kyi mgo can no //
NK015(ba)020:370: badz+ra kro d+ha ha a pa ra tsit+ta h'u /
NK015(ba)020:372: nub byang du khro bo chen po gzhan gyis mi thub pa dang /
NK015(ba)020:373: yum rdo rje mda' snyems ma /
NK015(ba)020:374: sprul pa spyang ki dang khra'i mgo can no //
NK015(ba)020:375: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h'u /
NK015(ba)020:377: byang du khro bo chen po bdud rtsi 'khyil pa dang /
NK015(ba)020:379: sprul pa seng ge dang pha wang gi mgo can no //
NK015(ba)020:380: badz+ra kro d+ha tre lo kya bi dza ya h'u /
NK015(ba)020:382: byang shar du khro bo chen po khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba dang /
NK015(ba)020:383: yum rdo rje gsod byed ma /
NK015(ba)020:384: sprul pa dom dang sre mong gi mgo can no //
NK015(ba)020:385: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa ba la h'u /
NK015(ba)020:386: s+pho ta s+pho ta h'u phata /
NK015(ba)020:387: nub tu khro bo chen po stobs po che dang /
NK015(ba)020:388: yum rdo rje bskul byed ma /
NK015(ba)020:389: sprul pa thugs kar h'u las so so'i sngags kyis bskor ba'o //
NK015(ba)020:390: khra thabs yab ni rang rang gi gtso bo la gzigs /
NK015(ba)020:391: yum ni 'dra ste yab la gzigs /
NK015(ba)020:393: dred dang byi ba'i mgo can no //
NK015(ba)020:394: khro bo bcu yang kun 'dra ba la /
NK015(ba)020:395: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog mthing nag /
NK015(ba)020:396: phyag na phur pa dril ba /

NK015(ba)020:1141: long ka srin po'i ngan sngags bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1142: bram ze'i ku dug drang srong dmod pa bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1143: rgya gar chos kyi sngags byad bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1144: rgya nag gtsug lag tsang kun bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1145: zhang zhung ngan sngags jo byol bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1146: khro bo'i ngan sngags rbod gtong bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1147: ge sar dmag gi dra bzhi bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1148: stag gzig nor gyi bla kheb bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1149: sum pa'i glang dmar bon zor bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1150: mu stegs ngan sngags bar bu bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1151: steng nyi zla gza' skar mkha' rgyu bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1152: 'og sa bdag klu gnyan gdug rtsub bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1153: klu bdud nag po'i gtad nan bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1154: ag+ne me yi sbyin bsreg bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1155: mi dang mi min thams cad kyi //
NK015(ba)020:1156: bsam sbyor gdug rtsub ngan pa bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1158: glo bur nyi khri chig stong dang //
NK015(ba)020:1159: bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1161: rlung mkhris bad kan 'dus pa dang /
NK015(ba)020:1162: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1163: sdang byed dgra bo'i steng du bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1164: gnod byed bgegs kyi steng du bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1165: phur kha bstan pa'i steng du bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1166: thun zor 'phen pa'i steng du bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1167: gtad mnan byed pa'i steng du bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1168: bsam sbyor ngan pa'i steng du bzlog /
NK015(ba)020:1169: bsgyur cig bzlog cig he ru ka /
NK015(ba)020:1170: khyed kyi thugs dam dus la bab //
NK015(ba)020:1171: bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK015(ba)020:1172: mthu dbang dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK015(ba)020:1174: bla ma dkon mchog yi dam mkha' 'gro chos skyong
NK015(ba)020:1175: srung ma dang bcas pa rnams dgongs su gsol lo
NK015(ba)020:1176: // spyir sangs rgyas kyi bstan dgra /
NK015(ba)020:1178: rdo rje slob dpon gyi sku dgra /
NK015(ba)020:1179: bdag cag rnal 'byor pa'i dgos dgra /
NK015(ba)020:1185: snga dgra lag gi byas pa /
NK015(ba)020:1186: phyi dgra yid la bsam pa /
NK015(ba)020:1187: da dgra thad du btsug pa /
NK015(ba)020:1192: byad ma gnod byed lha srungs dang bcas pa rnams /
NK015(ba)020:1193: bcom ldan 'das rgyal ba zhi khro'i lha tshogs rnams dang /
NK015(ba)020:1194: dpal ldan lha mo nag mo /
NK015(ba)020:1195: dpal ldan mgon po nag po /
NK015(ba)020:1196: 'chi bdag gis rgyal po gshin rje me ru rtse /
NK015(ba)020:1197: cho 'phrul rgyal mo re ma ti /
NK015(ba)020:1198: gza' bdud chen po ra hu la /
NK015(ba)020:1200: mthu che la rtsal drag pa khyed rnams kyi zhal du /
NK015(ba)020:1201: dmar gyi gtor ma 'di dang mnyam du bzhes shig /
NK015(ba)020:1208: las pa las la ma zhe na /
NK015(ba)020:1209: ling pa ling la ma zhe na /
NK015(ba)020:1211: pho nyas rgyug log ma byed /
NK015(ba)020:1212: nam mkha' stong pa la tshad ma btsug /
NK015(ba)020:1213: sa gzhi gro mo la rjes ma bzhag /
NK015(ba)020:1214: tshe phyi ma la dus ma btab /
NK015(ba)020:1215: lo dang zla bar ma bzhag la /
NK015(ba)020:1216: zhag dang za ma'i nang du sgrol cig /
NK015(ba)020:1217: de nas bzlog sngags bzlas pa'i gting la /
NK015(ba)020:1218: ye d+har+m+aa tshar gcig bzlas pas /
NK015(ba)020:1219: bsrung 'khor gyi tshul du lha tshogs rnams zhal nang du gyu bar bsgom la /
NK015(ba)020:1221: bdag ni rang rig ye shes blo dang ma ldan pas //
NK015(ba)020:1222: bag med tshul gyi dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK015(ba)020:1223: bka' brgyud bla ma'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK015(ba)020:1224: rdo rje slob dpon sku la bzod par gsol //
NK015(ba)020:1225: bdag ni rang rig ye shes blo dang ma ldan pas //
NK015(ba)020:1226: bag med tshul gyi dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK015(ba)020:1227: dpal chen he ru ka'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK015(ba)020:1228: thugs rje che mnga' rnams la bzod par gsol //
NK015(ba)020:1230: bdag ni rang rig ye shes blo dang ma ldan te //
NK015(ba)020:1231: bag med tshul gyi dam la 'gal gyur te //
NK015(ba)020:1232: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK015(ba)020:1233: ma sring rgya mtsho'i tshogs la bzod par gsol //
NK015(ba)020:1234: bdag ni rang rig ye shes blo dang ma ldan te //
NK015(ba)020:1235: bag med tshul gyis dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK015(ba)020:1236: chos skyongs srung ma'i thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK015(ba)020:1237: dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs la bzod par gsol //
NK015(ba)020:1238: gsang sngags rmad byung theg chen sgor zhugs rnal 'byor rnams //
NK015(ba)020:1239: lta ba 'phang dmas chos nyid don ma rtogs //
NK015(ba)020:1240: sgom pa yun thung yi dam lha ma 'dris //
NK015(ba)020:1241: spyod pa brlab chung yi dam lha ma mnyes //
NK015(ba)020:1242: sbyin pa stobs chung ser sna'i mdud ma grol //
NK015(ba)020:1243: bsam gtan stobs chung 'dod chags sems ma non //
NK015(ba)020:1244: snying rje shugs chung zhe sdang spro ma zhi //
NK015(ba)020:1245: shes rab blo chung gti mug mun ma sel //
NK015(ba)020:1246: ma mthong mthong gyi lha 'drer bskur btab sam //
NK015(ba)020:1247: ma nyes pa la sngags kyi zor thal lam //
NK015(ba)020:1248: ma rtogs pa la phur pa'i dbal thal lam //
NK015(ba)020:1249: sman med argasa yi dam lha mchod dam //
NK015(ba)020:1250: sta na byin gyis ma rlobs gnas 'khyams sam //
NK015(ba)020:1251: g+ha na byin gyis ma rlobs rul khyer ram //
NK015(ba)020:1252: dkyil 'khor bri nor mar me 'bar bsad dam //
NK015(ba)020:1253: phyi'i 'dul khrims ma srungs khrims nyams sam //
NK015(ba)020:1254: nang gi dam tshig ma srungs dam nyams sam //
NK015(ba)020:1255: bsrung mtshams ma mchis sdig dang gral gcig gi //
NK015(ba)020:1256: slob dpon bka' drin can gyi bka' bcag sam //
NK015(ba)020:1257: grogs mched khyad par can gyi thugs dkrugs sam //
NK015(ba)020:1258: dmag chen dpon byas ling chen kha bsgyur ram //
NK015(ba)020:1259: chu bsgyur me bkyes sems can srog bcad dam //
NK015(ba)020:1260: de la sogs te nyes sgrib ci mchis pa /
NK015(ba)020:1262: / 'phags pa mngon sum bzhugs pa'i spyan snga ru //
NK015(ba)020:1263: gnong 'gyod yid la dran te mthol zhing bshags //
NK015(ba)020:1264: bdag cag sems can lags pas ma rig 'khrul pa bgyi //
NK015(ba)020:1265: sgyu ma lags pas nongs pa rjes su bshags //
NK015(ba)020:1266: thugs rje chen po'i bzod pa dang du bzhes //
NK015(ba)020:1267: ye shes chen pos tshangs pa stsal du gsol //
NK015(ba)020:1268: yi ge brgya pa ci rigs pa 'don /
NK015(ba)020:1269: de nas bkra shis brjod pa ni /
NK015(ba)020:1270: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis bkra shis pa'i dgongs pa mdzad /
NK015(ba)020:1271: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis dbyangs mdzad /
NK015(ba)020:1272: lha dang lha mo rnams kyis me tog gi char phab /
NK015(ba)020:1273: chos skyong rnams kyis bar chad kyi bgegs bskrad par bsam la /
NK015(ba)020:1274: kun gyi me tog dkyil 'khor la gtor nas /
NK015(ba)020:1275: phun sum tshogs pa mnga' ba gser gyi ri bo 'dra /
NK015(ba)020:1277: / 'jig rten gsum gyi mgon po dri ma gsum spangs pa //
NK015(ba)020:1278: sangs rgyas pad+ma rgyas pa'i 'dab 'dra'i spyan mnga' ba //
NK015(ba)020:1279: de ni 'jig rten dge ba'i bkra shis dang po'o //
NK015(ba)020:1280: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK015(ba)020:1281: de yi nye bar bstan pa'i mchog rab mi g.yo ba /
NK015(ba)020:1283: / 'jig rten gsum na grags shing lha dang mis mchod pa //
NK015(ba)020:1284: chos kyi dam pa skye dgu rnams la zhi byed pa //
NK015(ba)020:1285: de ni 'jig rten dge ba'i bkra shis gnyis pa'o //
NK015(ba)020:1286: bkra shis dge 'dun dam pa chos ldan thos pa'i bkra shis phyug /
NK015(ba)020:1287: lha dang mi dang lha ma yin gyi mchod pa'i gnas //
NK015(ba)020:1288: tshogs kyi mchog rab ngo tsha shes dang dpal gyi zhing //
NK015(ba)020:1289: de ni 'jig rten dge ba'i bkra shis gsum pa'o //
NK015(ba)020:1290: bkra shis dam pa deng rgyal ba sras bcas bsod nams mthu dag dang /
NK015(ba)020:1291: lha rnams kun gyi basngagasa pa brjod pa dang //
NK015(ba)020:1292: gsang sngags rig sngags rnams kyi mthu stobs dang //
NK015(ba)020:1293: bden par smra ba rnams kyi bden tshig gi //
NK015(ba)020:1294: bkra shis bsod nams ri bo bzhin du brtan pa dang //
NK015(ba)020:1295: snyan pas nam mkha' bzhin du khyab pa dang //
NK015(ba)020:1296: rgyud 'dzin nyi zla bzhin du gsal ba ste //
NK015(ba)020:1297: bkra shis bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu zhi ba dang //
NK015(ba)020:1298: mi mthun gnod pa'i rkyen dang bral ba yi /
NK015(ba)020:1300: / 'dod pa 'grub cing phun sum tshogs pa ste //
NK015(ba)020:1301: bkra shis lo brgya thub cing ston brgya mthong ba dang //
NK015(ba)020:1302: tshe ring nad med bde skyid phun sum tshogs //
NK015(ba)020:1303: theg pa mchog la nges par 'byung ba yi //
NK015(ba)020:1304: bkra shis sbyin pa btang zhing tshul khrims bsrung ba dang //
NK015(ba)020:1305: bzod pa bsgom zhing brtson 'grus brtsams pa dang //
NK015(ba)020:1306: mnyam par 'jog cing shes rab bskyed pa yi //
NK015(ba)020:1307: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK015(ba)020:1308: sku lnga lhun grub rgyal ba rgya mtsho dang //
NK015(ba)020:1309: gsung lnga lhun grub dam chos rgya mtsho dang //
NK015(ba)020:1310: thugs lnga lhun grub rgyal sras smin pa'i tshogs //
NK015(ba)020:1311: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK015(ba)020:1312: bkra shis shing mi mthun pa'i phyogs thams cad las rgyal bar gyur cig /
NK015(ba)020:1313: rdo rje slob dpon sku tshe ring bar gyur cig /
NK015(ba)020:1314: dkyil 'khor gnyen po zhal gro bar gyur cig /
NK015(ba)020:1315: mched dang lcam dral thams cad la bar chad mi 'byung bar gyur cig /
NK015(ba)020:1317: mi dmigs pa'i ngang la rgyas gdab /
NK015(ba)020:1320: dge ba byang chub tu bsngo /
